空闲超时策略执行清理操作，帮助优化资源利用率，防止资源泄漏，并维护系统健康。\n  Line 9: 在 `pkg/agentd` 模块中实现空闲清理控制器，通过 client-go 库监控和管理 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 自定义资源，自动检测并清理长期空闲的资源，减少手动运维负担，提升集群资源利用效率。\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018 Implementation Summary\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/spec.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018 Specification\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/proposal.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/README.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018 Implementation Notes\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/CHANGE.md:\n  Line 1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n  Line 4: - **AR**: AR-018\n  Line 5: - **Title**: Agentd 空闲清理控制器","metadata":{"matches":19,"truncated":false},"title":"AR-018|空闲清理控制器","time":{"start":1775862702045,"end":1775862702062}}}}
