Found\n246: \n247: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_NotFound -v`\n248: \n249: ---\n250: \n251: ### Task 21: Implement controller unit tests - TestReconcile_MissingAnnotation\n252: - [ ] Create test for sandbox without last-activity-time annotation\n253: - [ ] Create sandbox resource without annotation\n254: - [ ] Verify Reconcile returns reconcile.Result{}, nil\n255: - [ ] Verify no requeue is triggered\n256: - [ ] Verify sandbox is not deleted\n257: \n258: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_MissingAnnotation -v`\n259: \n260: ---\n261: \n262: ### Task 22: Implement controller unit tests - TestReconcile_InvalidAnnotation\n263: - [ ] Create test for sandbox with invalid RFC3339 time format\n264: - [ ] Create sandbox resource with invalid annotation value\n265: - [ ] Verify Reconcile returns reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: 30s}\n266: - [ ] Verify error is returned with proper message\n267: - [ ] Verify sandbox is not deleted\n268: \n269: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_InvalidAnnotation -v`\n270: \n271: ---\n272: \n273: ### Task 23: Implement controller unit tests - TestReconcile_NotExpired\n274: - [ ] Create test for active sandbox (not expired)\n275: - [ ] Create sandbox resource with recent last-activity-time\n276: - [ ] Verify Reconcile returns reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: >0}\n277: - [ ] Verify RequeueAfter is time.Until(expirationTime)\n278: - [ ] Verify no error is returned\n279: - [ ] Verify sandbox is not deleted\n280: \n281: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_NotExpired -v`\n282: \n283: ---\n284: \n285: ### Task 24: Implement controller unit tests - TestReconcile_Expired\n286: - [ ] Create test for expired sandbox (>15 minutes idle)\n287: - [ ] Create sandbox resource with old last-activity-time\n288: - [ ] Verify Reconcile calls Delete on sandbox\n289: - [ ] Verify Reconcile returns reconcile.Result{}, nil\n290: - [ ] Verify no error is returned\n291: - [ ] Verify sandbox is marked for deletion\n292: \n293: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_Expired -v`\n294: \n295: ---\n296: \n297: ### Task 25: Implement controller unit tests - TestReconcile_DeleteFailure\n298: - [ ] Create test for delete operation failure\n299: - [ ] Setup fake client that returns error on Delete\n300: - [ ] Verify Reconcile returns error\n301: - [ ] Verify error is propagated correctly\n302: - [ ] Verify no requeue is triggered (error triggers automatic retry)\n303: \n304: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestReconcile_DeleteFailure -v`\n305: \n306: ---\n307: \n308: ### Task 26: Implement SetupWithManager test\n309: - [ ] Create test for SetupWithManager method\n310: - [ ] Verify controller is registered with manager\n311: - [ ] Verify Sandbox resource is watched\n312: - [ ] Verify no errors are returned\n313: - [ ] Use fake manager for testing\n314: \n315: **Verification**: Run `go test ./pkg/agentd -run TestSetupWithManager -v`\n316: \n317: ---\n318: \n319: ### Task 27: Add integration test - TestIdleCleanupE2E\n320: - [ ] Create end-to-end test using envtest\n321: - [ ] Create sandbox resource with last-activity-time annotation\n322: - [ ] Wait for 15 minutes (or use time manipulation)\n323: - [ ] Verify sandbox is deleted by controller\n324: - [ ] Verify proper cleanup occurs\n325: - [ ] Verify no errors in controller logs\n326: \n327: **Verification**: Run integration test with real Kubernetes API server (envtest)\n328: \n329: ---\n330: \n331: ### Task 28: Add integration test - TestActivityUpdate\n332: - [ ] Create end-to-end test for activity update\n333: - [ ] Create sandbox resource\n334: - [ ] Update last-activity-time annotation\n335: - [ ] Verify timer is reset\n336: - [ ] Verify sandbox is not deleted after original expiration\n337: \n338: **Verification**: Run integration test and verify activity update resets timer\n339: \n340: ---\n341: \n342: ### Task 29: Verify metrics.go