{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862763250,"sessionID":"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i","part":{"id":"prt_d79ab4ed1001YP9HmlLO0bLIfj","messageID":"msg_d79ab2dbc001nIqKE8783PJS9S","sessionID":"ses_28655b065ffe5esZZd4x0I346i","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-a77c0677ec4641109ce2cdc40afc0066","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: - **AR**: AR-018\n5: - **Title**: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n6: - **Module**: pkg/agentd\n7: - **Language**: Go\n8: - **Size**: S\n9: - **Status**: Pending\n10: \n11: ## Description\n12: [To be filled during spec definition]\n13: \n14: ## Dependencies\n15: [To be filled during spec definition]\n16: \n17: ## Related Changes\n18: [To be filled during spec definition]\n\n(End of file - total 18 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-018\n- **Title**: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n- **Module**: pkg/agentd\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Status**: Pending\n\n## Description\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Dependencies\n[To be filled during spec definition]\n\n## Related Changes\n[To be filled during spec definition]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-018/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775862763243,"end":1775862763249}}}}
